%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 90b1af8943794c7f870ab17e35297c59, type: 3}
  m_Name: IntroGardenDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: Oh... you're finally here. I've been waiting for you.
  - speakerName: Hero
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e142f5eb8d6e4de2a96b07cb34a2911, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 0
    text: Where am I...? What is this place?
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: This is your inner garden.
  - speakerName: Hero
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e142f5eb8d6e4de2a96b07cb34a2911, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 0
    text: It's... so empty. And everything's in ruins.
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: It wasn't always like this. The grown-ups who were meant to care for this
      place when you were little couldn't give it the care it needed.
  - speakerName: Hero
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e142f5eb8d6e4de2a96b07cb34a2911, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 0
    text: Is that why it looks like this?
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: Yes. Some plants withered away. Cracks spread through the ground. And some
      things never got the chance to grow at all.
  - speakerName: Hero
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e142f5eb8d6e4de2a96b07cb34a2911, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 0
    text: That's... really sad.
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: It is. But there's something you should know.
  - speakerName: Hero
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e142f5eb8d6e4de2a96b07cb34a2911, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 0
    text: What?
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: You're not a child anymore. Now you're the one who can bring this garden
      back to life.
  - speakerName: Hero
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e142f5eb8d6e4de2a96b07cb34a2911, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 0
    text: Do you really think I can?
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: I know you can. It won't happen overnight, though. We'll have to explore
      the garden, uncover what happened in each part of it, and slowly help it heal.
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: See that little tree? That's your inner tree. It's small now, but every
      challenge you overcome will help it grow stronger.
  - speakerName: Hero
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e142f5eb8d6e4de2a96b07cb34a2911, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 0
    text: So if I help the garden...
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: ...the tree will grow too. And so will you.
  - speakerName: Hero
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0e142f5eb8d6e4de2a96b07cb34a2911, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 0
    text: Then... let's do it.
  - speakerName: Bird
    speakerPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8bc7b80290a84470b8ede312550d16b6, type: 3}
    speakerOnRight: 1
    text: I'll be with you every step of the way. Come on.
